OL,7,FNewcastle United co-owners Amanda
OL,8,FStaveley and Mehrdad Ghodoussi are set
OL,9,Fto leave the club after three years at
OL,10,FSt James' Park, ITV News understands.
OL,12,FStaveley played a key role in
OL,13,Ffacilitating the Saudi Arabia Public
OL,14,FInvestment Fund's (PIF) #300million
OL,15,Ftakeover of the club in October 2021.
OL,17,FPIF purchased a 80% stake in Newcastle
OL,18,F- while the Reuban family hold a 10%
OL,19,Fshare in the club.
